<a href="/questions/496944-what-is-a-page-cutter-and-why-does">What *is* a page-cutter and why does Helene need one?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_496944'><a id="like_count_community_question_496944" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/496944?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">15 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F368916.84_Charing_Cross_Road">like</a></span>

