<li class='cover' id='bookCover_50370757'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/50370757"><img alt="ดัชเชสแห่งถนนบลูมสบรี" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1578581591l/50370757._SX98_.jpg" />
